---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About AmicBridge">
  <section style="padding: 3rem 1rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem;">About AmicBridge</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      AmicBridge is dedicated to helping investors discover real-world opportunities that can grow their wealth. 
      We don’t handle your money — we give you the knowledge and insights you need to invest smarter and 
      with confidence.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      Our focus is on identifying valuable assets such as apartments, real estate projects, and high-potential 
      investment opportunities across different markets. We analyze and track assets that can generate 
      stable income or appreciate quickly in value — turning information into opportunity.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      By subscribing to our insight platform, you gain access to exclusive data, reports, and expert evaluations. 
      Each opportunity is rated with a percentage score showing how likely it is to deliver high returns, 
      giving you clarity in a world full of uncertainty.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      AmicBridge is the bridge between you and smarter investing — helping you move from speculation 
      to strategy. Whether you’re looking for property investments or digital assets, we help you identify 
      where your money can work best for you.
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/membership" style="background: #0070f3; color: white; padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
        Get Access to Insights
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
